<p class="">Do I understand your Ruling, Sir Charles, to mean that I must not speak about the Co-operative societies?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-37d4b66f-1ff7-4055-a773-784f16aa9246" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
