<p class="">I was just about to stop the hon. and gallant Gentleman.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-11605d54-0db7-4bf0-9b7e-63433a881aa4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
