    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am obliged to the right hon. Member. The hon. Member (Mr. Lewis) was doubtfully in Order, so far as he had gone, but in any event was going into the subject in too much detail. His arguments were in danger of going too wide.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-32f6b6f4-9e65-45c0-aaa4-0efd9c5d21ab" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
